property_description: Live in the tree-tops with this amazing Sunol Woods view property. Believed to be originally built by the heirs of Charles Crocker in 1931 as a part of Kilkare Woods, a development of 100 12' X 16' cabins in the woods for middle class San Franciscans. Today, this property boasts breathtaking views of the surrounding woods, wildlife, and Sinbad Creek. It's been remodeled and expanded over the years and is now approximately 1, 928 sf. Located on the sunny and warm side of the ridge, the charming 2-level cottage has multiple patios, an enclosed porch, and was used for many years as a two level duplex with kitchen, laundry and full baths on both levels. Located just 10 minutes from Hwy 680 and only 30 minutes to Freemont, 2465 Kilkare is ideally situated as a weekend getaway property or a primary residence. This property is ready for a new owner to add a few fresh finishes to make it their own, or perhaps someone will opt to invest in a total remodel resulting in a stunning Kilkare Woods retreat ready for the next 100 years.
Directions to Property: From Downtown Sunol, North on Kilkare to address.

property_description: Welcome to this promising fixer-upper nestled in the heart of the vibrant Melrose District, just moments away from Mills College in East Oakland! This charming 3bd, 2-ba home invites investors and first-time buyers alike to unleash their creativity and vision. Boasting 1, 382 square feet of living space, this residence presents a canvas for transformation and customization. Original hardwood flooring awaits discovery beneath the carpeting in each bedroom, adding timeless allure to the home's interior. A cozy wood-burning fireplace graces the living room, offering warmth and ambiance on chilly evenings. The spacious formal dining room flows seamlessly into the kitchen and breakfast nook, creating an ideal layout for entertaining loved ones. Convenience meets functionality with a separate laundry room located at the rear of the property, adjacent to the kitchen. Outside, a large privately fenced driveway leads to a detached 2-car garage, which has been converted to provide additional space for various uses. Embrace outdoor living in the expansive low-maintenance backyard, perfect for hosting family BBQs and outdoor gatherings.
